title: Pavel Logačev, Ph.D.
text:
I’m a data scientist currently working on price optimization at Pearson Ham. Before that, I did a PhD in Cognitive Science at the University of Potsdam, and was an assistant professor at the Dept. of Linguistics at Bogazici University, Istanbul.
I’m interested in Bayesian modelling and non-parametric methods.
